__data__.text:
Last Updated: 10th Nov 2023

Track Access Management System 
(TAMS)  CCL  
Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)   
 
Question                                Answ er 
FAQ Type :1 Main Info  (5) 
What is Min. Consecutive?  If you select 3 dates of work and indicate “Min. 
Consecutive 2”, the engine can allocate either date1 & 
date2, or date2 & date3  
What is Any_Of_?  If you select 3 dates of work and indicate “Any 1 of 3”, 
the engine can allocate any 1 of the 3 selected dates  
Who to look for if I need to create new / edit / delete 
task type?  Please look for EWR Planning team  (CCL MOCC)  
What type of works impact continuity of 750V DC 
traction power?  Continuity of Power  refer  to the traction circuit 
integrity. If there is a disconnection of positive cables 
from the 3rd rail CT or the negative cables YBN from the 
running rails, Power Maintenance need to be informed 
to ensure that the traction circuit integrity is 
maintained before Pax service starts . 
What does the EWR number stand for?  Branch code + Task type code + YY + running number  
 
FAQ Type : 2. Sector  (3) 
Which fields are mandatory to fill in?  The fields that are marked with an asterisk are 
mandatory . 
How do I book CCL Extension Line (CBFT & CMRB)  Bound “EI” – Inner Bound of CCL Extension  
Bound “EO” – Outer Bound of CCL Extension  
How do I book double bound?  Bound “ IO” – Inner & Outer Bound  
Bound “EIO” – Inner & Outer Bound of CCL Extension  
 
FAQ Type :  3. Safety Protection (3)  
Can I leave any SCD fields blank if I do not want to install 
any thing at that power sector?  All fields have to be filled in by the cut -off time on the 
night of the work.  
Can additional SCDs (more than the required 2) be 
installed?  Yes, in graphic mode there is a SCD icon, drag and drop 
that icon on the power sector that you want the SCD to 
be installed.  Minimum 1 SCD is required for EWR.  
How to insert portable red flashing light, extra SCD, SCC, 
standing loco and standing train?  Select the respective icon in graphic mode, drag and 
place it on the booked sector or 3rd rail.

__data__.text:
Last Updated: 10th Nov 2023  
Version 1.0  
 
FAQ Type : 4. Manpower (2)  
I cannot find my name in the PM/PIC list?  Please check your PM/PIC validity and status  
Can I edit PM/PIC name and work party size on the 
AGAT?  Yes, please do the amendments on the AGAT before cut -
off time  
 
FAQ Type : 5 . AGAT (7)  
What can I amend in AGAT?  Book in/out station, safety protection, PM/PIC name, 
team size  
What is the cut -off time for amendment?  2330hrs. Please refer to OP for latest update  
How to print AGAT?  Select the AGAT, click on export and it will download as 
PDF. From there, you can print AGAT or save to 
computer  
Do I need to apply for AGAT after TAMS allocated my 
EWR?  No, AGAT will be automatically generated after EWR is 
allocated. However PM/PIC need to check that AGAT is 
correct. If not, make amendments before the cut -off 
time.  
 
AGAT generation time:  
Normal EWR: 2000hrs on the day of EWR meeting, 
Wednesdays and Fridays.  
Late and Urgent Requests: After the request has been 
approved  
Where to find my AGAT?  AGA Ts where you are the requestor or the PM/PIC, 
please click on the tab “My AGAT” in your homepage. 
Your AGATs will be displayed there . To search for AGATs 
that are created by others, click go to Execution > AGAT 
to search.  
When should I cancel EWR and AGAT?  If AGAT has not been generated yet (before 2000hrs on 
the day of EWR meeting, Wednesdays and Fridays), 
please cancel EWR.  
 
Once AGAT has been generated, please cancel AGAT 
(system will automatically cancel the related EWR).  
Do I need to print AGAT?  It is recommended to print AGAT, AGAT contains 
comprehensive information of the work which can help 
during toolbox briefing.  
 
FAQ Type: 6. Approving EWR  (2) 
If I assign multiple approvers to approve my EWR, do all 
of them need to approve?  1 approver to approve is sufficient  
Are approvers compulsory?  It is compulsory for late request and urgent request  
 
For normal EWR, please check with your department 
process.

What is particular user?  This feature is to add your colleague to be able to view

Why do I need to input my handphone number and
